Title: Love Scenery Season 1 Episode 03
Synopsis: is a 2021 Chinese television series directed by Qin Zhen, adapted from the novel 'A bright spear is easy to hide, but a secret love is hard to prevent' (明枪易躲，暗恋难防) by Qiao Yao. It starred Lin Yi and Xu Lu in the leading roles.
